TI  - A Supplementary Chemical Engineering Internship on Campus: Digital Twin of a 50 kt/y Ethyl Acetate Production Line
AU  - Liu, Boyang
AU  - Ding, Jie
AU  - Zhu, Tenglong
AU  - Jiao, Liang
AU  - Zhang, Shule
AU  - Zhong, Qin
PY  - 2026
