TI  - Problem-Based Modular Learning in Instrument Engineering Within Education 5.0
AU  - Demin, Aleksei
AU  - Vlasov, Andrey
AU  - Kuzmina, Natalya
AU  - Savenkov, Igor
AU  - Zemlyakov, Vladimir
AU  - Kuzmina, Svetlana
