TI  - VR Training Effectiveness Evaluation Based on Activity Data Analysis
AU  - Kubola, Kanuengnij
AU  - Jantarakongkul, Benchaporn
AU  - Boonmee, Prawit
AU  - Srithammee, Nattamon
AU  - Fongsamut, Chalermpan
